# Teamtailor API

The Teamtailor API is following the [JSON API Specification](http://jsonapi.org/).

If you have any question or feedback please contact us at [support@teamtailor.com](mailto:support@teamtailor.com)

### Example use cases:

* Build a custom career site. Display info about jobs, departments and locations.
* List current job openings
* Get detailed information about individual jobs
* Create new jobs
